data.text:
UPDATE 2: The event has been rescheduled as a breakfast meeting (8:30-10:00 am ET) on March 6, 2019, same location (City Club of Washington, 555 13th St., NW, Washington, DC).

UPDATE: This event was postponed due to the partial government shutdown.

Original entry: The Washington Space Business Roundtable (WSBR) will hold a luncheon on January 24, 2019 from 11:30 am – 1:30 pm ET at the City Club of Washington, 555 13th St., NW, Washington, DC. The speaker is Kevin O’Connell, Director of the Office of Space Commerce at the Department of Commerce.
